cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a novel privacy-preserving federated machine learning model, which is the main focus of the paper. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): The paper discusses data privacy and security as a sensitive topic and proposes a solution that applies local differential privacy. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses the challenge of handling scattered data and proposes a solution that involves processing the modeling jointly on different clients. 
- cs.DB (Databases): The paper discusses the challenge of centralizing data and proposes a solution that does not require exchanging any raw data. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses the challenge of deploying real-life AI applications in the current circumstances and proposes a solution that provides superior performance for machine learning.
